  <md:title>Work in the United States</md:title>
  <md:abstract><list>
<item>Describe the current U.S. workforce and the trend of polarization</item>
<item>Explain how women and immigrants have changed the modern U.S. workforce</item>
<item>Understand the basic elements of poverty in the United States today</item>
